        <h1 class="">Latest News &amp; Information</h1>
        <!-- Important Owl stylesheet -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://tb2cdn.schoolwebmasters.com/accnt_1/site_13146/Owl%20Carousel%20Plugin/OwlCarousel.css">
<!-- Default Theme --><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://tb2cdn.schoolwebmasters.com/accnt_1/site_13146/Owl%20Carousel%20Plugin/OwlTheme.css">
<div id="nt-container">
<div id="newsItem" class="owl-carousel owl-theme">
<div class="item" tabindex="0">           
		<div class="nt-title">May School Board Meetings</div>
		<p class="">The Smethport Area School District is planning to hold both the May 4, 2020 board of directors work session meeting and the May 11, 2020 board of directors voting meeting as scheduled in the elementary school LGI room. According to guidelines for public meetings/gatherings having fewer than 10 persons present, board members will participate via distance conferencing technology, and we will limit administrative attendance. </p>
<div><br></div>
		<a href="/news#MaySchoolBoardMeetings" class="readmore-link" aria-label="May School Board Meetings news article">Read more  <i class="fa fa-angle-double-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
</a>
	</div>
<div class="item" tabindex="0">           
		<div class="nt-title">School Closure</div>
		<p class="">On April 9, 2020, Governor Wolf announced that all Pennsylvania Schools will remain physically closed for the remainder of the 2019–2020 school year. </p>
		<a href="/news#SchoolClosure" class="readmore-link" aria-label="School Closure news article">Read more  <i class="fa fa-angle-double-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
</a>
	</div>
<div class="item" tabindex="0">           
		<div class="nt-title">Improved Access to Elementary Distance Learning Resources</div>
		<p class="">We are very excited to announce an improved way to access your student's at-home learning resources. Be sure to <a href="https://es.smethportschools.com/Distance-Learning" title="" alt="" target="_blank" class=""><a href="https://es.smethportschools.com/Distance-Learning" title="" alt="" target="_blank">visit our new Distance Learning page</a></a> to access Smethport Elementary learning activities for continuing education review and enrichment.</p>
		<a href="/news#elementarydistancelearning" class="readmore-link" aria-label="Improved Access to Elementary Distance Learning Resources news article">Read more  <i class="fa fa-angle-double-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
</a>
	</div>
<div class="item" tabindex="0">           
		<div class="nt-title">SASD Announces Phase III of Continuing Education Plan</div>
		<p class="">On April 1, 2020, the SASD launched phase III of our continuing education plan. Teachers, educational professionals, and education support professionals returned to active work status today to begin this process. Please take a moment to r<a href="https://tb2cdn.schoolwebmasters.com/accnt_524537/site_524538/Documents/Continuity-of-Education-Plan.pdf" title="" alt="" target="_blank">eview the Smethport Area School District continuity of education plan</a>.</p>
		<a href="/news#SASDAnnouncesPhaseIIIofContinuingEducationPlan" class="readmore-link" aria-label="SASD Announces Phase III of Continuing Education Plan news article">Read more  <i class="fa fa-angle-double-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
</a>
	</div>
<div class="item" tabindex="0">           
