        <h1 class="home">Welcome to Our District</h1>

        <p class="">Welcome to Smethport Area School District! Located in the beautiful Pennsylvania Wilds, we are a full-service, public school district in McKean County. Together, the two schools that comprise our district provide a safe, empowering learning environment
            for preschool through twelfth-grade students. </p>

            <p class="">Thank you for visiting. We are happy to provide you with information about <a href="/Our-District" title="" alt="" target="_self">our district</a>, <a href="/Our-Schools" title="" alt="" target="_self">our schools</a>, and the excellent programs and <a href="/Student-Services" title="" alt="" target="_self">services</a> we offer students. Go, Hubbers!</p>

                <h2 class="">A Message from Our Superintendent</h2>
                <p class=""><img src="https://tb2cdn.schoolwebmasters.com/accnt_524537/site_524538/Graphics/staff_DavidLondon_100819.jpg" alt="David London" class="float-right" style="width: 100%; max-width: 150px; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; margin-top: -1em;">Welcome, Hubbers!</p>

                    <p class="">We are proud to present our website to you as another communication vehicle where you can keep up to date and informed about all our amazing programs and activities. We’re excited about this school year and all the growth that entails. </p>

                        <p class="">Our initiative to “support the child, develop the student” is in full swing, and we want to say “thank you” for your support. You are a vital part of the educational process. Research shows that when parents are actively involved in school, their children are absent less often, behave better, and, therefore, achieve more. </p>
<p class="">Please take the time to <a href="https://tb2cdn.schoolwebmasters.com/accnt_524537/site_524538/Documents/March-2020-Superintendent-Newsletter.pdf" title="" alt="" target="_blank">view Mr. London's March Newsletter</a>.</p>

                            <p class="">Here’s to an amazing year of growth.</p>

                                <p class="">Sincerely,</p>

                                    <p class="signature"><a href="mailto:dlondon@smethportschools.com" title="" alt="" target="_top">David London</a></p>
